title: Counter-Strike 1.6
description: Counter-Strike 1.6 is a game based on Half-Life game ! All files are Steam RIP-ed with some visual adjustments. You can play this game for free now , downloading this version ! This version contains the latests files and all game clients was posted before to be made some updates . Some benefits : - You can save 10$ from buying the original game - 100% clean files - You can play on every server [ Steam & No-Steam ] - You can play with your friends [ Share with them this awesome client game ] - You can play in offline mode with bots - The client comes with a server list updated weekly - Just 234Mb installer path - The client comes with a new functions for joining automaticaly on a random server [ This save much time to select a good server ] - New GUI menu and background for a good visual looking Screen : https://imgur.com/a/Dqexw
